            <description>Mirrors engine.js age_appropriateness_check. Under-18 is a HARD_FAIL routed to in-person review (no paediatric dosing tables exist); an UNKNOWN age is NOT_RUN so no dose can reach a possible child. Pure age logic — no knowledge base.</description>
